{"_id":"class-sorcerer","name":"Sorcerer","type":"class","img":"icons/svg/aura.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Sorcerers cast arcane spells through inborn talent rather than study. They know a limited set of spells but can cast any of them without preparing in advance, and their power is keyed to Charisma.</p><h3>Alignment</h3><p>Any.</p><h3>Key Class Features</h3><ul><li><strong>Spells:</strong> Cast arcane spells from the sorcerer/wizard list spontaneously. Charisma-based (DC 10 + spell level + Cha modifier). Know a fixed number of spells per level; no preparation needed.</li><li><strong>Familiar:</strong> Obtain a familiar (24 hours, 100 gp). Familiar grants special abilities based on type and master level. Death or dismissal costs XP and cannot be replaced for a year and day.</li><li><strong>Spell Selection:</strong> Begin with four 0-level and two 1st-level spells; gain more at each level per table. At 4th and every even level, can swap one known spell for another of the same level.</li></ul><p>Sorcerers are not proficient with armor or shields; armor interferes with somatic components.</p>","hitDie":"d4","babProgression":"poor","saves":{"fort":"poor","ref":"poor","will":"good"},"skillPointsPerLevel":2,"classSkills":[{"key":"bluff","name":"Bluff"},{"key":"concentration","name":"Concentration"},{"key":"craft-alchemy","name":"Craft (Alchemy)"},{"key":"craft-armorsmithing","name":"Craft (Armorsmithing)"},{"key":"craft-bowmaking","name":"Craft (Bowmaking)"},{"key":"craft-weaponsmithing","name":"Craft (Weaponsmithing)"},{"key":"craft-trapmaking","name":"Craft (Trapsmithing)"},{"key":"knowledge-arcana","name":"Knowledge (Arcana)"},{"key":"knowledge-architecture-and-engineering","name":"Knowledge (Architecture and Engineering)"},{"key":"knowledge-dungeoneering","name":"Knowledge (Dungeoneering)"},{"key":"knowledge-geography","name":"Knowledge (Geography)"},{"key":"knowledge-history","name":"Knowledge (History)"},{"key":"knowledge-local","name":"Knowledge (Local)"},{"